answers.answer: Woohoo for January mommas!! The 17th right here :) woke up thinking of pancakes and bacon with o.j or cream of wheat with toast!! Too lazy and cold to get up though lol. I feel good though!! Anxious of course but energetic and feeling better then ever!! Merry Christmas!!!
Well I was duE jan 3 but I'll be having it within the next 3 hours
I'm due the 26th. 33 days until eviction day. I'm ready to get this child out of me so I can kiss her little cheeks! Merry Christmas to all, and I hope if we are traveling that it is safe!

Im due the 13th, only 20 days left! :)
